MADE-SHOT DETECTION:
- una vez tenemos el ring detection, crear dos cajas:
	- una encima del aro
	- otra debajo del aro
	
	la idea es que para que se considere canasta, deberá entrar en la primera caja, y en un cierto número de frames
	entrar en la siguiente caja
	
	se puede combinar con algun otro método de deteccion de canasta encestada para ser mas robusto (el resto de métodos 
	deben tener un porcentaje de acierto similar, o sino entonces ponderar los resultados)




import cv2
import streamlit as sl
from PIL import Image
import tempfile
import numpy as np
from domain_layer.domain_controller import DomainController
from streamlit_image_coordinates import streamlit_image_coordinates

sl.title("Statistics Generator")
sl.subheader("This app is for generating the statistics from a video, which will be shown in the Statistics Displayer")

video = sl.file_uploader("Upload file:")
if video is not None:
    tfile = tempfile.NamedTemporaryFile(delete=False)
    tfile.write(video.read())
    vf = cv2.VideoCapture(tfile.name)

    top_view_image_sl = sl.file_uploader("Upload minimap image:")
    if top_view_image_sl is not None:
        top_view_image = Image.open(top_view_image_sl)

        sl.write("Instructions:")
        sl.write("1. Click on the image to get pixel coordinates of the first component of the line.")
        sl.write("2. Release the mouse button to get pixel coordinates of the second component of the line.")

        sl.image(top_view_image, caption="Topview", use_column_width=True)
        img_array = np.array(top_view_image)
